Package: plotlyvis
Type: Package
Title: Create visually appealing charts using Plotly's R-API (plotly package) with an easy to use interface
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Riddhiman", "Roy", email = "riddhiman.roy@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package provides wrapper functions for plot_ly() (from the plotly package) to help make presentation worthy 
			 charts with minimal effort.
